	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(ID_DONAN_TOWER, LOC_DONAN_RTC, "NPC_WALK_FAST", true)

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	
	Hydra.ActorEnable(ID_HAMMER_END)
		
	--Donan + Taissa Walk & Fade
	Hydra.ActorWarpToActor(ID_TAISSA_TOWER, LOC_TAISSA_RTC_FIN)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(ID_TAISSA_TOWER, LOC_TAISSA_EXIT, "NPC_WALK_FAST", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(ID_TAISSA_TOWER, LOC_TAISSA_EXIT)
	
	Hydra.ActorWarpToActor(ID_DONAN_TOWER, LOC_DONAN_RTC_FIN)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(ID_DONAN_TOWER, LOC_DONAN_EXIT, "NPC_WALK_FAST", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(ID_DONAN_TOWER, LOC_DONAN_EXIT)
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(ID_DONAN_TOWER)
	
	Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(ID_TAISSA_TOWER, 1)
	Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(ID_DONAN_TOWER, 1)
	Hydra.EventSend("VERGE6_COMPLETE")
	
end
